{
  "stem": "471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, look, here's 100 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have to locate them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to put them in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to give them room to live.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Food, they're going to get it on the job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's the way it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, as time goes by, they were cleaning up ghetto, they were making the ghetto smaller, deportation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Smaller the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They make a Ghetto A-- a Ghetto A, a Ghetto B.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Meantime, they were building, on the main Plaszow, barracks already.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They made Plaszow-- if I said, this was located right on the spot where, before the war, there was a new Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "On that cemetery, they built the-- the barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And believe you me, the first barrack that was finished, they took the hundred people from ghetto and sent them up there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was-- there was a guard still under supervised-- supervision, excuse me-- from Miller, from downstairs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because, you see, Julag was downstairs, down-- down below on the main highway.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this was up in the hill a little bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But we were working and going from over there to Kabel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "To-- to Kabelwerker.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] All of a sudden, they built, they built, they put more people from the ghetto up to Plaszow there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were bringing them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was making smaller.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Some of them, they went to Auschwitz, some of them, they were here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Oh, I forgot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My brother, let him rest in peace.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I went to Kabelwerker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my-- and-- and-- and my brother went to Stalowa Wola, another camp someplace else, more east.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So we got separated, you see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I lost track of him.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
